tweet: SEO Tip - Register your domain name for multiple years. Domain age and period of registration are factors in search engine algorithms.
SEO Tip - Use your most important keywords as file names, including images.
SEO Tip - When writing text for your pages, try not to repeat non-keywords on the same page.
SEO Tip - Update your site regularly and keep increasing your index with relevant pages. Search engines reward these.
SEO Tip - Build additional pages as landing pages to target additional keywords/phrases. Include them in your sitemap files.
